/taylor-swift-adds-two-new-london-eras-shows-with-paramore-3538573">在伦敦温布利体育场进行八场演出</a>。</p></div></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/detroit-jingle-ball-announced-taylor-swift-as-surprise-guest-before-bringing-out-impersonator-3555326">《底特律叮当球》宣布泰勒·斯威夫特为惊喜嘉宾，随后</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上首次出现模仿者。</p> ;
